<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p>We run local.starflow.uk to share local info. We collect minimal analytics (GA4) to understand traffic. We do not sell personal data.</p>
<h2>Cookies & Analytics</h2>
<p>We use cookies only after you give consent via our cookie banner. Analytics are used to measure page views and improve content.</p>
<h2>Advertising</h2>
<p>We use Google AdSense. Ads may use cookies to show more relevant ads after consent.</p>
<h2>Links to other sites</h2>
<p>We link to third-party sites. Their content and privacy practices are separate.</p>
